data.text:
4 days ago

Funeral held for woman killed by police after calling 911, deputy facing murder charges

A funeral is being held Friday for Sonya Massey, an Illinois woman shot and killed by police after calling 911 for help.

5 days ago

Man fatally shot by out-of-town officers near Republican convention identified

Officers with the Columbus Police Department responded to the incident on Tuesday.

5 days ago

Child left in hot SUV while mom shopped at Walmart: report

Newly released bodycam video shows police officers in Florida consoling a young child who had been left alone in a hot car.

6 days ago

Seattle police chief fires officer who made 'limited value' comments after student's death

Jaahnavi Kandula was a graduate student at Northeastern University in Seattle when she was hit and killed in January 2023.

6 days ago

Family of woman fatally shot by deputies expected to meet with police, view bodycam video

The family of an Illinois woman shot and killed by police is holding a news conference Thursday and is expected to view the body camera video from the shooting.

11 days ago

Officer video shows police finding boy in SUV after theft attempt that killed his mother

Officer body-camera video shows the moment Columbus police found a boy who was inside his mother's SUV shortly after it was stolen.

18 days ago

VIDEO: Suspect in stolen forklift leads police on 'chase' in Florida, authorities say

A man driving a stolen forklift led police in Florida on a "slow speed pursuit" across the Three Mile Bridge on the Fourth of July, according to authorities.
